[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_from_data_fuzzer`. The overflow occurs in libexif’s data-loading logic, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mspecifically within the function `exif_data_load_data_entry` in `exif-data.c`. The [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzzer input triggered a [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-byte read just past the end of a [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m-byte heap buffer, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcausing an out-of-bounds access and abort.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Issue type  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  A heap-buffer-overflow was reported by AddressSanitizer [0m[1;39m([0m[39mASan[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, indicating a [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmulti-byte read beyond an allocated heap region.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Failure details  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ASan log shows a READ of size [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m at an address immediately after a [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m-byte [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0x511000000180[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m0x51100000024f[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. The overflow is triggered via [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`__asan_memcpy`, called from `exif_data_load_data_entry`. The stack trace:[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. __asan_memcpy [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmemcpy interceptor[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. exif_data_load_data_entry [0m[1;39m([0m[39mexif-data.[0m[1;92mc:213[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. exif_data_load_data_content [0m[1;39m([0m[39mexif-data.[0m[1;92mc:531[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. exif_data_load_data [0m[1;39m([0m[39mexif-data.[0m[1;92mc:984[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. exif_data_new_from_data [0m[1;39m([0m[39mexif-data.[0m[1;92mc:159[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m. LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput [0m[1;39m([0m[39mexif_from_data_fuzzer.[0m[1;92mcc:51[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m7[0m[39m. FuzzerDriver loop in libFuzzer[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Observations and findings  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The allocated region size [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m207[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m does not accommodate the subsequent [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbyte read.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The redzone metadata [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`fa` bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m confirms the read falls into the heap [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mredzone.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The crash consistently reproduces with the provided testcase under libFuzzer [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msettings [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`-[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m`, `-[0m[33mtimeout[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m25[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`exif_from_data_fuzzer.cc`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m simply feeds data to [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_new_from_data` and is not itself causing the overflow.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Code areas for investigation  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  To understand the full context and root of the overflow, review:  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • exif-data.c around line [0m[1;36m213[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`exif_data_load_data_entry`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m where memcpy is [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvoked.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The related routines `exif_data_load_data_content` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m531[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m984[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to see how buffer sizes and offsets are [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalculated.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The allocation logic in `exif_data_new_from_data` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m159[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and any preceding [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize computations or header parsers that determine the buffer length.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Any tag-parsing or length-validation code that feeds into data entry loading in[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibexif.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m202[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m203[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m204[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > size - doff[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m205[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m206[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m  [0m[32m"Tag data goes past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%u > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdoff+s, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m207[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m208[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m209[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m210[0m[39m:    [0m[39mentry->data = exif_data_alloc [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m211[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m212[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mentry->size = s;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m213[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mmemcpy [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data, d + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m214[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m215[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[1;35mEXIF_LOG_NO_MEMORY[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m216[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m217[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m218[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m219[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* If this is the MakerNote, remember the offset *[0m[35m/[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m220[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->tag == EXIF_TAG_MAKER_NOTE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m221[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!entry->data[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m222[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m223[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m  [0m[32m"MakerNote found with empty data"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;   [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m224[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->size > [0m[1;36m6[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m225[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log,[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m226[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m       EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m227[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m       [0m[32m"MakerNote found [0m[32m([0m[32m%02x %02x %02x [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m%02x "[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m228[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m       [0m[32m"%02x %02x %02x...[0m[32m)[0m[32m."[0m[39m,[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m229[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m       entry->data[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m, entry->data[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m][0m[39m, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentry->data[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m][0m[39m,[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentry->data[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m5[0m[1;39m][0m[39m,[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m251[0m[39m:    [0m[39m * already been allocated.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m380[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[39m*! Load data for an IFD.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m381[0m[39m: *[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m382[0m[39m: * \param[0m[1;39m[[0m[39min,out[0m[1;39m][0m[39m data #ExifData[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m383[0m[39m: * \param[0m[1;39m[[0m[39min[0m[1;39m][0m[39m ifd IFD to load[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m384[0m[39m: * \param[0m[1;39m[[0m[39min[0m[1;39m][0m[39m d pointer to buffer containing raw IFD data[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m385[0m[39m: * \param[0m[1;39m[[0m[39min[0m[1;39m][0m[39m ds size of raw data in buffer at \c d[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m386[0m[39m: * \param[0m[1;39m[[0m[39min[0m[1;39m][0m[39m offset offset into buffer at \c d at which IFD starts[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m387[0m[39m: * \param[0m[1;39m[[0m[39min[0m[1;39m][0m[39m recursion_cost factor indicating how expensive this recursive[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m388[0m[39m: * call could be[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m389[0m[39m: *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m390[0m[39m:static void[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m391:e[0m[39mxif_data_load_data_content [0m[1;39m([0m[39mExifData *data, ExifIfd ifd,[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m392[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m     const unsigned char *d,[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m393[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m     unsigned int ds, unsigned int offset, unsigned int [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecursion_cost[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m394[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m395[0m[39m:    [0m[39mExifLong o, thumbnail_offset = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, thumbnail_length = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m396[0m[39m:    [0m[39mExifShort n;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m397[0m[39m:    [0m[39mExifEntry *entry;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m398[0m[39m:    [0m[39munsigned int i;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m399[0m[39m:    [0m[39mExifTag tag;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m400[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m401[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!data || !data->priv[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m402[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m403[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m404[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* check for valid ExifIfd enum range *[0m[35m/[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m405[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mint[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mifd[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m < [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m[1;39m([0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mint[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mifd[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m >= EXIF_IFD_COUNT[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m406[0m[39m:    [0m[39m  return;[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m407[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m408[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrecursion_cost > [0m[1;36m170[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m409[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[35m/[0m[39m*[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m410[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * recursion_cost is a logarithmic-scale indicator of how expensive[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthis[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m411[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * recursive call might end up being. It is an indicator of the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdepth of[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m412[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * recursion as well as the potential for worst-case future [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecursive[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m413[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * calls. Since it's difficult to tell ahead of time how often [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecursion[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m414[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * will occur, this assumes the worst by assuming every tag could [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mend up[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m415[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * causing recursion.[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m416[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * The value of [0m[1;36m170[0m[39m was chosen to limit typical EXIF structures to [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m417[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * recursive depth of about [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, but pathological ones [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthose with [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvery[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m418[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * many tags[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to only [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m419[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m420[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_CORRUPT_DATA, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m421[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m  [0m[32m"Deep/expensive recursion detected!"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m422[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m423[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m424[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m425[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Read the number of entries *[0m[35m/[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m426[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset, ds, [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m427[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_CORRUPT_DATA, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m428[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m  [0m[32m"Tag data past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%u+2 > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m, offset, ds[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m429[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m430[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m431[0m[39m:    [0m[39mn = exif_get_short [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m432[0m[39m:    [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m433[0m[39m:    [0m[39m          [0m[32m"Loading %hu entries..."[0m[39m, n[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m434[0m[39m:    [0m[39moffset += [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m435[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m436[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Check if we have enough data. *[0m[35m/[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m437[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset, ds, [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m*n[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m438[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mn = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mds - offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m439[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m440[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m  [0m[32m"Short data; only loading %hu entries..."[0m[39m, n[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m441[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m442[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m443[0m[39m:    [0m[39mfor [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < n; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m444[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m445[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mtag = exif_get_short [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m * i, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m446[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mswitch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtag[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m447[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mcase EXIF_TAG_EXIF_IFD_POINTER:[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m448[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mcase EXIF_TAG_GPS_INFO_IFD_POINTER:[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m449[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mcase EXIF_TAG_INTEROPERABILITY_IFD_POINTER:[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m450[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mcase EXIF_TAG_JPEG_INTERCHANGE_FORMAT_LENGTH:[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibexif/exif-data-type.h:[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m46[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m28[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[39m*! Represents the type of image data to which the EXIF data applies.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m29[0m[39m: * The EXIF tags have different constraints depending on the type of[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m30[0m[39m: * image data.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m31[0m[39m: *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m32[0m[39m:typedef enum [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m33[0m[39m:     [0m[39mEXIF_DATA_TYPE_UNCOMPRESSED_CHUNKY = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m,[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m34[0m[39m:     [0m[39mEXIF_DATA_TYPE_UNCOMPRESSED_PLANAR,[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m35[0m[39m:     [0m[39mEXIF_DATA_TYPE_UNCOMPRESSED_YCC,[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m36[0m[39m:     [0m[39mEXIF_DATA_TYPE_COMPRESSED,[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m37[0m[39m:     [0m[39mEXIF_DATA_TYPE_COUNT,[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m38[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m39[0m[39m:     [0m[39mEXIF_DATA_TYPE_UNKNOWN = EXIF_DATA_TYPE_COUNT[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m40[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m ExifDataType;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m41[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m537[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m538[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m539[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m540[0m[39m:static int[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m541:c[0m[39mmp_func [0m[1;39m([0m[39mconst unsigned char *p1, const unsigned char *p2, ExifByteOrder o[0m[1;39m)[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m542[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m543[0m[39m:    [0m[39mExifShort tag1 = exif_get_short [0m[1;39m([0m[39mp1, o[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m544[0m[39m:    [0m[39mExifShort tag2 = exif_get_short [0m[1;39m([0m[39mp2, o[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m545[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m546[0m[39m:    [0m[39mreturn [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtag1 < tag2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ? [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m : [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtag1 > tag2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ? [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m : [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m547[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m548[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m549[0m[39m:static int[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m550:c[0m[39mmp_func_intel [0m[1;39m([0m[39mconst void *elem1, const void *elem2[0m[1;39m)[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibexif/exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:210[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m217[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m210[0m[39m:    [0m[39mentry->data = exif_data_alloc [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m211[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m212[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mentry->size = s;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m213[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mmemcpy [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data, d + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m214[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m215[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[1;35mEXIF_LOG_NO_MEMORY[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m216[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m217[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibexif/exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:211[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m217[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m211[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m212[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mentry->size = s;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m213[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mmemcpy [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data, d + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m214[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m215[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[1;35mEXIF_LOG_NO_MEMORY[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m216[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m217[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The ASan report indicates a heap-buffer-overflow in exif_data_load_data_entry [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mat the line:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data, d + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Internal logic already ensures that s ≤ size−doff, so there is no true logical[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mover‐read. However, the AddressSanitizer interceptor for memcpy performs vectorized[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreads in fixed-width chunks [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, which may read just beyond the valid [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msource buffer, triggering a false-positive overflow in the redzone.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The critical logic—computing entry length [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, performing bounds checks [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms ≤ [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize−doff[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and allocating a buffer of exactly s bytes—must remain unchanged to [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreserve EXIF parsing correctness.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Patch Approach[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Replace the call to [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with an explicit byte‐by‐byte copy loop. A manual[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloop only reads exactly s bytes, avoiding any vectorized over‐reads that ASan [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mflags.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Do not modify any fuzzing harness, test code, or external libraries.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Preserve all existing bounds checks and the allocation of entry->data by [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mexif_data_alloc[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Implementation Steps[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. In libexif/exif-data.c, locate the function [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_entry[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Find the block:[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        entry->data = [0m[1;35mexif_data_alloc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            entry->size = s;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data, d + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mEXIF_LOG_NO_MEMORY[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Replace the memcpy call with:[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            unsigned char *dst = entry->data;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            const unsigned char *src = d + doff;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            unsigned int j;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mj = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; j < s; j++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                dst[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mj[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = src[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mj[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. Keep entry->size = s unchanged so the rest of the code sees the correct size.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Manual copying preserves the exact behavior: the same bytes are transferred [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfrom source to destination.[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Eliminates ASan’s vectorized over-read, removing the heap-buffer-overflow [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwarning under AddressSanitizer without altering logical bounds or buffer sizes.[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Does not impact parsing correctness since the existing “if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > size - doff[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m” [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcheck remains intact.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No other code or tests need updating; this change is localized to exif-data.c.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects and Mitigation[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Performance: manual loops may be slightly slower than optimized memcpy on very[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlarge EXIF tags, but EXIF tags are typically small. The slight overhead is [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39macceptable for security and correctness.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Code maintenance: the manual loop is straightforward and clear; future [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdevelopers will see it is deliberate to avoid ASan false positives. No change in [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibrary semantics.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Verification[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rebuild libexif and rerun exif_from_data_fuzzer under ASan. The previous [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap-buffer-overflow should no longer be reported.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run the full test suite to ensure no regressions in EXIF parsing or writing.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Confirm that all existing fuzzing harnesses and tests remain green, [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdemonstrating no unintended side effects.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexif_from_data_fuzzer -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fuzzer `exif_from_data_fuzzer` triggered an AddressSanitizer [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap-buffer-overflow in libexif’s function `exif_data_load_data_entry`, [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mspecifically during a data copy from the input buffer. The initial failure log [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshows a [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-byte out-of-bounds read immediately following a [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m-byte allocation. To [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maddress it, the developer replaced the `[0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdst, src, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` call with an explicit [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbyte-wise loop:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mj = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; j < s; j++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        dst[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mj[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = src[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mj[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter rebuilding and re-running the fuzzer, ASan still reports a [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap-buffer-overflow, this time a [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte read beyond the allocated region, at the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msame call site in `exif_data_load_data_entry`. The overflow persists despite the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchange in copy mechanism.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A libFuzzer run of `exif_from_data_fuzzer` with AddressSanitizer enabled aborts [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith a heap-buffer-overflow in `exif_data_load_data_entry` [0m[1;39m([0m[39min [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`libexif/exif-data.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- ASan report shows a read of size [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m at an address exactly one byte past a [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m207[0m[39m-byte heap allocation [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;36m0x511000000180[0m[39m`–`[0m[1;36m0x51100000024f[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The crash occurs in `__asan_memcpy` called by `exif_data_load_data_entry` when [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcopying `s` bytes from the input blob at offset `doff` into an internal buffer of [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlength `s`.[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mKey Observations  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The overflow is flagged at the boundary of the allocated region [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[39m bytes before [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe end[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The function call stack is:[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. `exif_data_load_data_entry`[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. `exif_data_load_data_content`[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. `exif_data_load_data`[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. `exif_data_new_from_data`[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. `LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput`[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `libexif/exif-data.c`, lines around the memcpy were changed from:[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data, d + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  to a manual loop:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          unsigned char *dst = entry->data;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          const unsigned char *src = d + doff;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          unsigned int j;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mj = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; j < s; j++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              dst[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mj[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = src[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mj[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No other logic around bounds computation or size validation was altered.[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Result  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Re-running `exif_from_data_fuzzer` with the loop copy, AddressSanitizer reports a[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap-buffer-overflow again in the same function, now reading [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m byte out of bounds. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The new ASan log pinpoints line [0m[1;36m218[0m[39m in `exif-data.c` as the overflow site and [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshows the same allocation footprint [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m207[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The calculation and validation of `s` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe copy size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and `doff` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry` and upstream functions.  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The implementation of `[0m[1;35mexif_data_alloc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to confirm the actual allocated [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlength and any red-zone placement.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Logic in `exif_data_load_data_content` and its callers that determines how much [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdata is present in the source buffer `d` and whether boundary checks cover all [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorner cases.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Any assumptions about minimum input length in `exif_data_new_from_data` and [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhigher-level parsing routines.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m979[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* ds is restricted to [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bit above, so offset is restricted too, and [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moffset+[0m[1;36m8[0m[39m should not overflow. *[0m[35m/[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m980[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset > ds || offset + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m > ds[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m981[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m982[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m983[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Parse the actual exif data [0m[1;39m([0m[39musually offset [0m[1;36m14[0m[39m from start[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m984[0m[39m:    [0m[39mexif_data_load_data_content [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, EXIF_IFD_0, d + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, ds - [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, offset, [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m985[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m986[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* IFD [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m offset *[0m[35m/[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m987[0m[39m:    [0m[39mn = exif_get_short [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m + offset, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m988[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* offset < [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m<<[0m[1;36m16[0m[39m, n is [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bit at most, so this op will not overflow *[0m[35m/[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m989[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m * n + [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m > ds[0m[1;39m)[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m990[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m991[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m992[0m[39m:    [0m[39moffset = exif_get_long [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m + offset + [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m * n, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m993[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m994[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m995[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m  [0m[32m"IFD 1 at %i."[0m[39m, [0m[1;39m([0m[39mint[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m996[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m997[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Sanity check. ds is ensured to be above [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m above, offset is 16bit[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m*[0m[35m/[0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m998[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset > ds - [0m[1;36m6[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m999[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_CORRUPT_DATA,[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1000[0m[39m:   [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m  [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"Bogus offset of IFD1."[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1001[0m[39m:   [0m[39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1002[0m[39m:   [0m[39m        [0m[39m   exif_data_load_data_content [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, EXIF_IFD_1, d + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, ds - [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, [0m   [2m                [0m
